headline: Starbucks: Turnaround Brewing, But Margin Squeeze And Valuation Keep Me At A Hold
summary: Starbucks shows margin pressure, premium valuation, modest growth, weak dividend trends, cash flow issues and a rangebound outlook. See why SBUX stock is a hold.
